    "attributes": {
        "action": "Higher tax on income of \u00a3400,000, and exit tax if they move to another country",
        "additional_details": "The top 10% own more wealth than 50% of the country. \r\n \r\nIf those earning over \u00a3400,000 wish to leave the country, we think there should be an exit tax equal to 5 years of tax",
